@startuml Diagrama de Capas - Clean Architecture
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam rectangleRoundCorner 15

title Diagrama de Capas - Arquitectura Limpia (Clean Architecture)

rectangle "**Capa de Presentación**\nCochera.Web (Blazor Server)" #E3F2FD {
    rectangle "Razor Components\n(Pages, Layout)" as Razor #BBDEFB
    rectangle "SignalR Hub\n(CocheraHub)" as HubLayer #BBDEFB
    rectangle "Web Services\n(SesionNotification,\nUsuarioActual)" as WebSvc #BBDEFB
}

rectangle "**Capa de Worker**\nCochera.Worker" as WorkerLayer #F3E5F5 {
    rectangle "MqttWorker\n(BackgroundService)" as MqttW #CE93D8
    rectangle "SignalRNotificationService\n(Hub Client)" as SignalRSvc #CE93D8
}

rectangle "**Capa de Aplicación**\nCochera.Application" as AppLayer #E8F5E9 {
    rectangle "Interfaces de Servicio\n(ICajonService, ISesionService,\nIEventoSensorService, etc.)" as AppInterfaces #A5D6A7
    rectangle "Implementaciones de Servicio\n(CajonService, SesionService,\nEventoSensorService, etc.)" as AppServices #A5D6A7
    rectangle "DTOs\n(CajonDto, SesionDto,\nEventoSensorDto, etc.)" as DTOs #A5D6A7
}

rectangle "**Capa de Dominio**\nCochera.Domain" as DomainLayer #FFF3E0 {
    rectangle "Entidades\n(Usuario, Cajon, Sesion,\nPago, EventoSensor, etc.)" as DomEntities #FFE0B2
    rectangle "Enums\n(EstadoCajon, EstadoSesion,\nMetodoPago, TipoEvento)" as DomEnums #FFE0B2
    rectangle "Interfaces de Repositorio\n(IRepository<T>, IUnitOfWork,\nICajonRepository, etc.)" as DomInterfaces #FFE0B2
}

rectangle "**Capa de Infraestructura**\nCochera.Infrastructure" as InfraLayer #FFEBEE {
    rectangle "Entity Framework Core\n(CocheraDbContext,\nMigraciones)" as EF #FFCDD2
    rectangle "Repositorios\n(Repository<T>, UnitOfWork,\nCajonRepository, etc.)" as Repos #FFCDD2
    rectangle "Servicios MQTT\n(MqttConsumerService,\nMqttSettings)" as MqttSvc #FFCDD2
    rectangle "RabbitMQ\n(RabbitMqManagement)" as RabbitSvc #FFCDD2
}

' === DEPENDENCIAS (Dirección de la flecha = "depende de") ===
Razor -down-> AppInterfaces : usa
Razor -down-> DTOs : consume
HubLayer -down-> DTOs : transmite
WebSvc -down-> AppInterfaces : usa

MqttW -down-> AppInterfaces : usa
MqttW --> MqttSvc : consume mensajes

AppServices -down-> DomEntities : mapea
AppServices -down-> DomInterfaces : usa
AppInterfaces <|.. AppServices : implementa

Repos -up-> DomInterfaces : implementa
Repos --> DomEntities : persiste
EF --> DomEntities : mapea
MqttSvc --> DTOs : produce

' === REGLA DE DEPENDENCIA ===
note right of DomainLayer
  **Regla de Dependencia:**
  - Domain NO depende de nada externo
  - Application depende solo de Domain
  - Infrastructure implementa interfaces de Domain
  - Web/Worker dependen de Application
  
  **Inversión de Dependencias (DIP):**
  Las capas superiores definen interfaces,
  las capas inferiores las implementan.
end note

note bottom of InfraLayer
  **Tecnologías Infrastructure:**
  - Entity Framework Core 8 (ORM)
  - Npgsql (PostgreSQL driver)
  - MQTTnet 4.3 (cliente MQTT)
  - RabbitMQ.Client 6.8 (AMQP)
end note

@enduml
